Content ideas




 → US02 — Select university on registration 
As a new user, I want to select my university from a list during registration so that I see content relevant to my institution. 
→ US03 — User role selection
As a new student, I want to select my role during registration so that the system personalises my experience
→ US05 — Login with email and password 
As a user, I want to log in using my university email and password so that I can securely access my account 
→ US06 —

As a user, I want the system to reject unrecognised email domains so that only valid university members can register

FR02 - Video library 

→ US07 — Lecturer upload teaching video 
As a lecturer, I want to upload a teaching video with a title, subject, and topic so that students can access my content anytime
→ US08 — Browse videos by subject and topic 
As a student, I want to browse videos organised by subject and topic so that I can find content relevant to what I am studying
→ US09 — Videos ranked by likes 
As a student, I want to see videos ranked by number of likes so that the highest quality content appears first
→ US10 — Like or dislike a video 
-As a student, I want to like or dislike a video so that I can rate the quality of the content
→ US11 — Comment on a video
As a student, I want to comment on a video so that I can ask questions and discuss the topic with peers
→ US12 — View individual video page
As a student, I want to view a video on its own dedicated page so that I can watch it without distractions

FR03 - Notes library 

US13 - Upload notes 
As a student, I want to upload my notes organised by subject and topic so that peers can find and benefit from them
US14 - Browse notes 
As a student, I want to browse notes organised by subject and topic so that I can find relevant study materials
US15 - See progress bar 
As a student,  I want to see a progress bar showing how close am I to receiving a certificate so that I stay motivated to contribute quality content
US16 - Receive Consistency excellence certificate 
As a student, I want to receive a Consistency Excellence Certificate when I upload 15 high quality notes in a year so that my contributions are formally recognised


FR04 - past year papers 

US17 - Upload past year papers 
As a lecturer, I want to upload past year examination papers organised by subject and year so that students can access them easily
US18 - Browse past year papers 
As a student, I want to browse past year papers filtered by subject and year so that I can find the right papers to practice for exam preparation
US19 - Download past year papers as pdf 
As a student, I want to download past year papers so that I can edit them, and study them offline 

FR05 - Interactive quiz 
US20 - Select subject and topic 
As a student, I want to select a subject and topic before starting a quiz so that I can practise the specific area I am studying
US21 - Answer interactive quiz 
As a student, I want to answer interactive quiz so that I can actively recall information
US22 - View quiz result 
As a student, I want to view quiz result so that I can refer back to those the question I want to revise
US23 -  Progress bar of interactive quiz 
As a student, I want a progress bar to keep track with the interactive quiz I’ve done for each subject

Earn badges 
As a student, I want to earn badges based on my quiz performance so that my achievements are recognised

Leaderboard 
As a student, I want to view a leaderboard showing top performers so that I can see how I rank among my peers

Practice module 

Exam format practice questions organised by chapter 
As a student, I want to access exam-format practice questions organised by chapter so that I can prepare practically for exams
Download practice module as pdf 
As a student, I want to download practice questions so that I can attempt them offline
Upload answer schemes for practice
As a lecturer, I want to upload answer schemes for practice questions so that students can refer to the correct answers after attempting them

Lecturer consultation booking 

Edit consultation timeslot 
As a lecturer, I want to add or cancel my consultation timeslots so that I can manage changes to my availability
available lecturer consultation timeslot 
As a student, I want to view available lecturer consultation timeslots so that I can find a suitable time to book
Book consultation timeslot 
As a student, I want to book a consultation timeslot so that I can get academic help from my lecturer
Received confirmation notification after booking 
As a user, I want to receive a confirmation notification after booking a consultation so that both parties are informed

Schedule Planner 

Set assignment deadlines 
As a student, I want to add assignment deadlines to my schedule planner so that I can track my upcoming submissions
Set examination dates 
As a student, I want to add examination dates to my schedule planner so that I can prepare in advance
Set personal academic task 
As a student, I want to add personal academic activities to my schedule so that I have a complete view of my commitments
Set upcoming deadlines and events in a place 
As a student, I want to view all upcoming deadlines and events in one place so that I can manage my time effectively
Consultation bookings automatically appear in my schedule planner
As a student, I want consultation bookings to automatically appear in my schedule planner so that my calendar stays up to date

Dashboard 

total points earned 
As a student, I want to see my total earned points on the dashboard so that I can track my quiz performance at a glance
earned badges 
As a student, I want to see my earned badges on the dashboard so that my achievements are visibly recognised
weekly ranking 
As a student, I want to see my current weekly ranking on the dashboard so that I am motivated to improve my position
weekly schedule 
As a student, I want to see my schedule for the current week on the dashboard so that I have an immediate overview of my upcoming commitments
total number of videos uploaded 
As a lecturer, I want to see the total number of videos I have uploaded on my dashboard so that I can monitor my content contributions
upcoming consultation of the week 
As a lecturer, I want to see how many students have booked my consultation slots on my dashboard so that I can prepare accordingly
Weekly schedule 
As a lecturer, I want to see my weekly schedule on the dashboard so that I can plan my availability


